{"tid":1162542,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"譚惠珠：修例草案直上大會非常合理　時間上理所當然","createTime":"2019-05-20T02:40:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-20T13:41:03.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"85443818f9203d2bb85066cc6f18e46c1d3b99b6","tid":1162542,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T02:40:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190520/s00001/3d961377e142f733a4eeee3d407d909f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190520%2Fs00001%2F3d961377e142f733a4eeee3d407d909f.jpg&h=66236dc3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n修訂《逃犯條例》爭議不斷，基本法委員會副主任譚惠珠出席港台節目時表示，感覺如今修例草案直上立法會大會的機會比較大，因現時已沒有其他途徑處理爭議，有關做法亦是大會規程容許。她表示，如政府現時決定將草案直上大會，是非常合理，在時間上也是理所當然的選擇，草案直上大會後，往後所有討論程序，亦會與以往的一樣。<br />\n<br />\n至於坊間有關先行處理台灣殺人案的建議，譚惠珠稱，沒聽到中聯辦有提過有關議題，但特區政府已屢屢回應上述建議不可行，相信中聯辦都會支持政府決定。<br />\n<br />\n至於中聯辦表態後，修例是否仍有調整空間，譚惠珠表示：「坊間提出的建議，如果政府已經解釋了做不到的理由，那麽我覺得中聯辦的立場便是支持政府依法施政。」不過，她強調中聯辦表態絕對不是等同草案不能修改，認為中聯辦僅是希望將有關議題納回正軌。<br />\n<br />\n至於有議員憂慮修例落實後美國將取消香港的特別地位，譚惠珠稱修例是按照聯合國範本執行，而且美國本身已與中國簽署引渡協議，雙方已有多次合作。她反問美國，若借修例責罰香港的道理何在，「是否你做就可以，香港做就不可以」。<br />\n<br />\n譚惠珠又以澳門和新加坡為例，稱澳門《基本法》23條本地立法已過10年，如今美國也沒有取消澳門的特別地位；新加坡方面，她形容新加坡的政治紅線眾所周知比香港更「硬」，但美國與新加坡的關係卻非常良好。因此，譚惠珠認為大家不要被政治理由和外界因素影響，呼籲大家心平氣和討論，強調現時港府修例每一步都是跟足國際標準。"},{"pid":"94575719e381db6055756f6e714f8efed7d7b451","tid":1162542,"uid":20933,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T02:40:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190520/s00001/1558317603353/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190520%2Fs00001%2F1558317603353%2F&d=3iEKCEnQ8TgOeM43nfYZ1zC6QH3F2wvzJ1VFJz7MVw4%3D&h=bc68afa0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190520%2Fs00001%2F1558317603353%2F&h=63a557d4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190520/s00001/1558317603353/</a>"},{"pid":"6855f8e169f31e36ede1dbfb9f0bebdb25638b53","tid":1162542,"uid":203417,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T02:42:51.000Z","msg":"咁都唔係跳曬啲step啦"},{"pid":"e80ceb2c7c3fb6ccff3fa05ef4bd75a12234040c","tid":1162542,"uid":53278,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T02:51:51.000Z","msg":"問隻肥豬一定係話中央有理架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢個位根本求其搵個呀婆都做得"},{"pid":"4db5b581c09db4a532d9c51b8c1ff6594b982e31","tid":1162542,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T12:50:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5db8e7b1d06c203754c956797350a9b1cb6c9f54","tid":1162542,"uid":171389,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T12:53:48.000Z","msg":"我阿嫲同佢一樣樣，好可惜佢亂講野，無人送終"},{"pid":"27a324bb48f94e3b1ee42afe264f882e36fa41a7","tid":1162542,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T12:57:09.000Z","msg":"好撚樣衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f23b9633296db878f7e99a8f5fb0c853be16acd","tid":1162542,"uid":15730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e80ceb2c7c3fb6ccff3fa05ef4bd75a12234040c","tid":1162542,"uid":53278,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T02:51:51.000Z","msg":"問隻肥豬一定係話中央有理架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢個位根本求其搵個呀婆都做得"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T13:03:46.000Z","msg":"係 咩都say yes就得"},{"pid":"81fb2cdbc6964df5904d05ed6a55793c11bfdb67","tid":1162542,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T13:06:45.000Z","msg":"見再佢個樣就諗起保皇狗"},{"pid":"8485ed5f70165c1a258f710c272d01a8e4d4a0ac","tid":1162542,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T13:29:01.000Z","msg":"基本法22條<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n中聯辦<br />\n<br />\n中聯辦<br />\n<br />\n中聯辦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一下唔記得咗一國兩制，要象徵式提下立法會添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac0ed4a7568b728d9ae360d415cc3a046d2d48c8","tid":1162542,"uid":65061,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T13:37:43.000Z","msg":"何方妖孽？"},{"pid":"870b8b1ccbe96cda9ba60497edc9d19f3f4265f7","tid":1162542,"uid":176442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T13:37:59.000Z","msg":"who are u?"},{"pid":"eed595cca1283c8b7c7a2ce791efbaa40debd824","tid":1162542,"uid":67338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T13:40:55.000Z","msg":"你班友大陸話要乜都話岩架啦"},{"pid":"d5dc3de326505942081e21dbfd6ba20fbc6b9909","tid":1162542,"uid":34213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T13:41:03.000Z","msg":"我都誠心希望佢冇人送終"}]}